  "title": "DESIGNATING THE MONTH OF FEBRUARY 2026, AS \"EATING DISORDERS AWARENESS AND PREVENTION MONTH\" IN DELAWARE.",
  "from_organization": "~{\"classification\": \"upper\"}",
